Zone

A zone may be determined either by:

  • Zone.areas being a MultiPolygon
  • Zone.center being a Point + Zone.distance being a distance, in meters. In the second case, a circle will be drawn around Zone.center with a radius of Zone.distance. For MySQL reasons, both fields are required to be NOT NULL.
